{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I would say that I was very disappointed that-- I liked it in England, really.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by that time, yes, they were playing sports, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, generally, I liked Uncle Rudi and Lotte.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Lotte, perhaps I should have said, was a-- was a great cook, especially in the cakes department, like the cake that we had at lunchtime today.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was probably from Lotte-- the recipe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I enjoyed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I liked England.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, And I think I was disappointed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On the other hand, I suppose, we missed our father, although he was more of a disciplinarian and all that kind of stuff compared with Uncle Rudi.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But, no, I think the family had to get together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, obviously, my father, for some reason or another, couldn't come to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, he, he should have come and joined us, really, rather than us joining him in Holland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On the other hand, Holland was, in 1936, perhaps perceived to be reasonably OK because there was really no idea that Hitler and the Nazis would invade Holland, that in-- by 1936.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the first World War, Holland had remained neutral.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They kept out of it-- out of the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, even those people who thought that there might be another war with the Nazis and all that, nobody thought that Holland would get involved.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we thought we'd be fairly safe-- obviously, safer in England, but reasonably safe in Holland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
